Title: [ANN] [CANLEAD] - ğŸ”¥ğŸš€ A SMARTER WAY TO SHARE AND EARN ğŸ”¥ğŸš€ğŸŒ - [CANLEAD]
Body: >>> By using your platform or app would every customer will get an effective method for acquisition and conversion in referral marketing? And when will your platform be available for alpha and beta testing?  Referral Marketing - Canlead allows the Host (Marketer) to create their product / service profiles and advertise them on the platform. The Leader (Referrer) who is either in the Host Community or not in the Host Community can view / refer the Candidate (friend / connection) to the Host. The Host pays the Leader in Fiat or Crypto after the referral transaction is completed. The Reputational system requests each user to rate each other then send the CAND tokens to each user - this method will incentivise the users to continue sharing their opportunities and making referrals on the platform. Please read the pitch deck for more info https://drive.google.com/file/d/1d9rXxDlaVSTJUlMn4zBZgEKcT_VJ6QC-/view?usp=sharing  What Mark Zuckerberg say about referral marketing , https://www.marke2ing.com/5-tactics-for-b2b-referral-marketing-success/  The App is available https://app.canlead.io please try to sign up next week as we have brought it down this week for some maintenance work.

Author: micquan
Title: [ANN] [CANLEAD] - ğŸ”¥ğŸš€ A SMARTER WAY TO SHARE AND EARN ğŸ”¥ğŸš€ğŸŒ - [CANLEAD]
Body: Canlead offers three user profiles or roles Host (customer), Leader (recruiter / agent) and Candidate (seeker) to simulate a real-world scenario or situation. Anyone can sign up and switch to the user role he wants to play depending on his situation. If he wants to make money then he becomes a Leader, if he wants to share / post the opportunity (job or service) then he becomes the Host or if he is seeking for a unique opportunity (job or service) then he becomes the Candidate. Note Host pays Leader a referral fee and Candidate gets the job. It works like Airbnb but with an extra role 'Leader' and Canlead has developed its own unique Brokerage Sharing Economy 2.0 model where all users are rewarded with tokens after the rating / deal has completed - refer to canlead.io for more info!!!!!
